@startuml PartyLifecycleStateDiagram

title Party Lifecycle State Management

' Define the starting point
[*] --> DRAFT

' 1. Intake & Validation States
state DRAFT #F9F9F9 : Initial record creation\n(Manual or SyntheticGen)
state PENDING_VERIFICATION #FFF2CC : Awaiting ID, Tax, or\nBusiness validation
state REJECTED #FFD9D9 : Validation failed\n(Invalid Tax ID/Identity)

' 2. Operational States
state ACTIVE #D5E8D4 : Verified and usable\nfor all business roles
state INACTIVE #F5F5F5 : Valid entity, but\nnew activity restricted

' 3. Administrative & Maintenance States
state PENDING_MERGE #DAE8FC : Identified as duplicate\nawaiting consolidation
state MERGED #E1D5E7 : Secondary record redirected\nto primary partyKey

' 4. Terminal / Compliance States
state DECEASED_DISSOLVED #EAEAEA : Individual passed or\nOrganization dissolved
state ARCHIVED #EAEAEA : Historical record only
state PURGED #FAEAEA : PII removed for GDPR/CCPA\n(Terminal State)

' --- Transitions ---

' A. Verification Path
DRAFT --> PENDING_VERIFICATION : Submit for vetting
PENDING_VERIFICATION --> ACTIVE : Verification successful
PENDING_VERIFICATION --> REJECTED : Verification failed
REJECTED --> DRAFT : Corrected and resubmitted

' B. Operational Lifecycle
ACTIVE --> INACTIVE : Business relationship paused
INACTIVE --> ACTIVE : Relationship resumed
ACTIVE --> DECEASED_DISSOLVED : Legal notification received

' C. Data Governance (MDM)
ACTIVE --> PENDING_MERGE : Duplicate detected
DRAFT --> PENDING_MERGE : Duplicate detected
PENDING_MERGE --> MERGED : Merge logic executed
MERGED --> [*] : Pointer persists in DB

' D. Archival & Privacy
INACTIVE --> ARCHIVED : Retention period reached
DECEASED_DISSOLVED --> ARCHIVED : Post-settlement archival
ARCHIVED --> PURGED : Privacy request / Global expiry
PURGED --> [*] : End of record lifecycle

' E. Global Exit
ACTIVE --> [*]
ARCHIVED --> [*]

@enduml